  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the value of postoperative troponin in the prediction of
      mid term and long term mortality and morbidity in children with congenital heart disease
      undergoing cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
